name: Earl Robles
text: Apparrently, there is such a thing as "notional agreement" ( 13 minutes is all I got.  5 million dollars has been transferred to your account).  We programmers don't like that because it makes grammar  fall out of our "rule-based" algorithm model. It is no longer syntactic   :)   https://stroppyeditor.wordpress.com/2013/12/16/a-number-of-people-doesnt-understand-notional-agreement/
